This style should be used as a standard style for windows that'll be created in future.
It has been created for optimization for our code, because some people love adding borders everywhere, some have weird StackPanel
fetish, etc. I don't have any troubles with this at all, but when there are too many of them, we have a perfomance problem in 
our app. - Kott.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
